[SHORT DESC]
The user always moves first, and flinches the foe. Can only be used on the first turn out.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Attacks with priority. Flinches the target. Can only be used on the first turn out. Switching the user back in will allow it to be used again.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/mach_punch">Mach Punch</a> is a Fighting-type equivalent, but can be used every turn and does not flinch.<br />
<a href="/rs/moves/quick_attack">Quick Attack</a> is almost identical, but can be used every turn and does not flinch.</p>